  "detailed_description": "<h1>NEW REQUISITION VR</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730650/extras/a885dd1b9ed3e18ac48a16777411cff9.avif?t=1761632865\" width=610 height=120 /></span><br><strong>Rebuilt from the ground up. New Extraction mode, new enemies, new weapons, <br>and cross-play with Meta Quest. Launching November 2025.</strong></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CRAFT ULTIMATE WEAPON</h2>Unleash your creativity by crafting crazy things<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730650/extras/6ad3cc02364084bf2f10b89490de2bd4.poster.avif?t=1761632865\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730650/extras/6ad3cc02364084bf2f10b89490de2bd4.webm?t=1761632865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730650/extras/6ad3cc02364084bf2f10b89490de2bd4.mp4?t=1761632865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PHYSICS-BASED MULTIPLAYER</h2>Everything in the game has a physical simulation<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730650/extras/f575b2d7068ce4c75685bffcb569ed12.poster.avif?t=1761632865\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730650/extras/f575b2d7068ce4c75685bffcb569ed12.webm?t=1761632865\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1730650/extras/f575b2d7068ce4c75685bffcb569ed12.mp4?t=1761632865\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAME MODES:</strong></h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Survival mode</strong><br></li><li><strong>Horde Mode</strong><br></li><li><strong>Story Mode</strong><br></li><li><strong>PVP</strong></li></ul>",
